room_title: Escape room "The Deadly Double Agent" by Arkansas Escape Rooms in Little Rock
room_address: 2615 North Prickett Road, Suite 4 Bryant, AR 72022
room_description: The destruction of the United States Embassy in the Capital of the Draconian Empire has caused worldwide panic. The Draconian security forces have learned the identity of 10 CIA agents undercover in the country. To stop the impending war, you must infiltrate their headquarters and destroy any evidence incriminating the agents.
